column1: queries

PREFIX  dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX  dbpr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>

SELECT DISTINCT  ?x2 ?x0 ?r0 ?r34 ?r48
WHERE
  { ?x2       rdf:type  dbpo:Film .
    dbpr:Casablanca
              ?r0       ?x2 .
    ?x0       rdf:type  dbpo:Person ;
              ?r34      <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casablanca_(film)> .
    dbpr:Author  ?r48   dbpo:Type
  }

PREFIX  grs:  <http://www.georss.org/georss/>
PREFIX  dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX  dbpr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>

SELECT  *
WHERE
  { dbpr:Paraguay
              rdf:type      dbpo:Place ;
              dbpo:capital  ?capital .
    ?capital  rdf:type      dbpo:PopulatedPlace ;
              grs:point     ?coord
  }

PREFIX  :     <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX  owl:  <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT  ?p
WHERE
  { :Johnny_Cash  ?p    ?CS .
    :Carl_Perkins
              ?p        ?CS .
    ?p        rdf:type  owl:ObjectProperty .
    ?CS       rdf:type  owl:Thing
  }

PREFIX  :     <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX  owl:  <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT  ?p
WHERE
  { ?CS  ?p        :Johnny_Cash ;
         ?q        :Eddie_Bond .
    ?p   rdf:type  owl:ObjectProperty .
    ?q   rdf:type  owl:ObjectProperty .
    ?CS  rdf:type  owl:Thing
  }

PREFIX  rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX  owl:  <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT  ?domain ?r ?ra
FROM <http://dbpedia.org/ontology>
WHERE
  { ?r       rdf:type     owl:ObjectProperty ;
             rdfs:domain  ?d ;
             rdfs:range   ?ra .
    ?domain  rdfs:label   ?d
  }

PREFIX  :     <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX  owl:  <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT  ?p
WHERE
  { ?CS  ?p        :Johnny_Cash ;
         ?p        :June_Carter_Cash .
    ?p   rdf:type  owl:ObjectProperty .
    ?CS  rdf:type  owl:Thing
  }
